snippet.textDisplay: It's mostly agreed by biographers that Poe and Virginia's relationship was completely innocent and that they acted almost like siblings or just best friends. Theres even a quote from someone saying she used to see them skipping and playing in the streets together... so yes still incredibly strange but I don't think anyone was being harmed. I live down the street from the building where they had their honeymoon, it was owned by Poe's friend Hiram Haynes and it was converted into a sweet little coffeeshop/library (unfortunately it closed a few years ago) and the owner allowed me upstairs to see where they stayed, it was pretty incredible.

snippet.textDisplay: If you're looking for more cases, I have a local one that actually made national news! The disappearance of Megan Nichols. She was a 15 year old girl who disappeared in 2014 and her remains were found in a field in 2018. It may help us find out what really happened to her! I know so many of us need our questions answered, having it on this show may help us find someone who knows something.
